    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/NGj9KLJ3aMwNQNozt039lg9q/15.0_pp_554_632_Interference_and_diffraction_with_partially_coherent_light.pdf\">15.0_pp_554_632_Interference_and_diffraction_with_partially_coherent_light.pdf</a><br>\nApologies if anything's unclear, maybe it's easier if I just upload the chapter, what I'm looking for is essentially section 10.2</p>",
